All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
Ant
Represents an Ant that can move in a world represented by a graph of different vertices
Anthill
Represents an abstract Anthill, a type of Vertex which is a home to many ants Subclasses myst implement specific behaviour for sending ants
AntPanel
Represents a panel to display information about living ants and buttons to kill them
Blue_Ant
Represents a Blue Ant, subclass of an Ant, that can move in a world represented by a graph of different vertices
Blue_Anthill
Represents a Blue Anthill, subclass of an Anthill, which is a type of vertex which is a home o many blue ants
Blunderer
Represents a Blunderer, a special type of Collector ant which in turn is a subclass of Red Ant Blunderer can move in a world represented as a graph of different vertices and collect larvae from them During its return to anthill it can leave some larvae on the path home
Collector
Represents a Collector subclass of Red Ant Collector can move in a world represented as a graph of different vertices and collect larvae from them
Drone
Represents a Drone, a subclass of Blue Ant Drone can move in a world represented as a graph of different vertices
LarvaeLabel
Represents a label to display the amount of larvae stored on a given Vertex
Leaf
Represents a Leaf, a type of Vertex on which no fighting can happen
Main
Entry point of the simulation Initializes and runs the world simulation
Panel
Represents a panel with buttons for sending ants from anthills
Red_Ant
Represents a Red Ant, subclass of an Ant, that can move in a world represented by a graph of different vertices
Red_Anthill
Represents a Red Anthill, subclass of an Anthill, which is a type of vertex which is a home o many red ants
Soldier
Represents a Soldier, subclass of Red Ant Soldier can move in a world represented as a graph of different vertices and attack blue ants
Sprite
Represents a Sprite, graphical representation of all objects in the simulation
Stone
Represents a Stone, a type of Vertex that cannot be walked through
Vertex
Represents a Vertex, the main part of the graph representing the world of the Ants.
Worker
Represents a Worker, a subclass of Blue Ant Drone can move in a world represented as a graph of different vertices and collect larvae from them Additionally it can attack red ants
World
Represents the World of Ants, the environment in which the Ant fight for food
